MAUI SHORT RIBS
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Marinate:
- 2 cups soy sauce
- 1.25 cups water
- 0.75 cups rice vinegar
- 1 tbsp sesame oil
- 4.5 tsp fish sauce
- 3.5 cups packed dark brown sugar
- 4 tbsp finely grated ginger (skin on)
- 1-2 tbsp finely grated garlic (peeled)

Meat:
- 6 pounds bone in beed short ribs (1/2 in)

Prep:
- Mix and marinate for 24 hours

